  <brief_title>Intramuscular Injection of Mesenchymal Stem Cell for Treatment of Children With Idiopathic Dilated Cardiomyopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Intramuscular Injection of Umbilical Cord Mesenchymal Stem Cell on the Ventricular Function of Children With Idiopathic Dilated Cardiomyopathy</official_title>
